<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Small Token Of Love</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>

    <div id="page-intro" class="card active">
        <div class="img-wrapper">
            <img src="https://i.ibb.co/6R2F8T6F/39048.jpg" alt="Your Picture" class="cat-img">
            <span class="heart-badge">👑</span>
        </div>
        <h1>So... I have something to tell you.</h1>
        <p class="sub-text">Ready for a life update? ✨</p>
        <button class="action-btn" onclick="nextPage('page-trust')">👆 Tap to Begin</button>
    </div>

    <div id="page-trust" class="card">
        <img src="https://i.ibb.co/VWVw83gS/39046.jpg" alt="Your Picture" class="cat-img">
        <p class="subtitle">This isn't something I say lightly—just a feeling from my heart—</p>
        <h2>Do you trust me?</h2>
        <div class="btn-row">
            <button class="btn-yes" onclick="nextPage('page-choose')">Yes, I do! 🦖</button>
            <button class="btn-no" id="btn-trust-no" onmouseover="moveButton(this)" onclick="moveButton(this)">No 🙈</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="page-choose" class="card">
        <div class="doodle-container">
            <div class="drawing-box" id="drawingBox">
                <img src="https://i.ibb.co/9HwNBy7K/39047.png" alt="Together Picture" class="main-doodle" id="doodleImg">
            </div>
        </div>
        <h2>One more thing...</h2>
        <p class="prompt-text">My heart already chose you... did yours choose me too? 💕</p>
        <div class="btn-row">
            <button class="btn-yes" onclick="triggerHandSlap()">Yes, I love you! 💖</button>
            <button class="btn-no" id="btn-choose-no" onmouseover="moveButton(this)" onclick="moveButton(this)">No 🥺</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="page-final" class="card">
        <img src="https://i.ibb.co/6R2F8T6F/39048.jpg" alt="Your Picture" class="cat-img">
        <p class="subtitle">One last thing... this is the most important question I'll ever ask.</p>
        <h2>Will you be mine—today, tomorrow, and forever? 💕</h2>
        <div class="btn-row" id="final-btn-row">
            <button class="btn-yes" onclick="nextPage('page-success')">Yes, forever! ❤️</button>
            <button class="btn-no" id="btn-final-no" onclick="showModal()">Let me think... 🤔</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="popup-modal" class="modal-backdrop">
        <div class="modal-box">
            <h2>Just Say YES! ❤️</h2>
            <p>Not because I'm asking, but because your heart is already answering. Don't let doubt steal a moment meant for us.</p>
            <div class="modal-btns">
                <button class="btn-yes" onclick="forceYes()">❤️ Yes, I'll Say YES! ❤️</button>
                <span class="fake-link" onclick="handleFakeLink()">Let me think...</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="page-success" class="card">
        <img src="https://i.ibb.co/VWVw83gS/39046.jpg" alt="Your Picture" class="cat-img">
        <h1 class="yay-title">YAYYYYY ❤️✨</h1>
        <h2>Now you're officially mine forever 💕</h2>
        <p class="sub-text">This is the beginning of our cutest love story ever 📝🎀</p>
        <button class="long-action-btn" onclick="nextPage('page-universe')">There's still more of my heart left to show you... 👇</button>
    </div>

    <div id="page-universe" class="card universe-theme">
        <div class="stitch-frame">
            <img src="https://i.ibb.co/9HwNBy7K/39047.png" alt="Together Picture" class="universe-img">
        </div>
        <h2>Every moment with you feels like my favorite universe ✨💫</h2>
        <button class="action-btn-universe" onclick="nextPage('page-letter')">💖 See My Message 💖</button>
    </div>

    <div id="page-letter" class="card">
        <h2>This is just for you...</h2>
        <div class="letter-icon-box">💌</div>
        <button class="action-btn" onclick="nextPage('page-letter-open')">Tap to see what's inside</button>
    </div>

    <div id="page-letter-open" class="card letter-pad">
        <h2 class="letter-header">To My Favorite Person ❤️</h2>
        <p class="letter-body">Every little moment with you feels magical. You make my ordinary days feel special, my smile softer, and my heart happier. ✨</p>
        <p class="letter-body">I don't know what the future holds, but if you're in it... I already know it'll be beautiful.</p>
        <p class="letter-body font-weight-bold">Thank you for existing ❤️</p>
        <button class="boom-button" onclick="nextPage('page-canvas')">Boom 💥</button>
    </div>

    <div id="page-canvas" class="card clear-bg">
        <canvas id="heartCanvas"></canvas>
        <div class="dashboard">
            <button class="ctrl-btn" onclick="resetCanvas()">🔄 Restart</button>
            <div class="speed-container">
                <label>Speed: </label>
                <input type="range" id="speedSlider" min="10" max="250" value="110">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
